{"tid":1317620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下小額錢債點搞","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T19:48:39.000Z","uid":198258,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3b269859075741f2b54703ed169730d0e50468","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:46:49.000Z","msg":"發夢買左物資送上去，留左陣睇人拆野。<br />\n夜啲仲未有衝突就去左新城食飯，有信用卡單。<br />\n之後狗衝左入黎圍，我就好驚好嬲，佢地一層一層咁上黎我壓力超大，我家姐打比我問有冇事我驚到喊。最後狗上到同一層，我有諗頭大叫一聲係你地逼死我咖然後跳落去，不過之後後面有人話呢到有路快啲走我就走左。<br />\n絕對冇打過狗/破壞野，就係係咁鬧狗，傳物資，叫呢到要人。<br />\n<br />\n本有抑鬱症，焦慮。有精神科醫生轉介信寫左我食緊咩藥，有大學心理輔導跟開。<br />\n<br />\n今次之後覺得食左三，四個月藥，輔導全功盡廢。高壓，恐懼，失眠，發夢比人拉左。個時好驚好驚好驚比人圍上黎拉走。好驚/絕望點解我食個飯會比人話非法集合，接受唔到。<br />\n<br />\n總之就係我嚇到痴左線。<br />\n<br />\n要搵邊個？點搞？"},{"pid":"2128503839ee99097406edfddac01109a1c1eabe","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:50:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人差唔多情況呀？"},{"pid":"effc4fbcfb588311e3b16ebaccca7e3179f7d095","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:50:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d4f9d1e35318ce4d9b0381bd33411c11658bf7c","tid":1317620,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eca341fba854f2926347adfab87faf0a37c9582","tid":1317620,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"傻豬，邊個搞成你咁？<br />\n唔係你自己啊<br />\n係呢個殘酷嘅政權啊<br />\n輔導教你改變自己，<br />\n但冇教你點樣喺對抗政權"},{"pid":"77d62898a925d411fe4226267bdcdef568869d68","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7eca341fba854f2926347adfab87faf0a37c9582","tid":1317620,"uid":174174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"傻豬，邊個搞成你咁？<br />\n唔係你自己啊<br />\n係呢個殘酷嘅政權啊<br />\n輔導教你改變自己，<br />\n但冇教你點樣喺對抗政權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:57:09.000Z","msg":"佢個仆街商場放狗入黎嚇我唔洗還呀？"},{"pid":"3e729463d6484c20adec6931299c37a2252fb274","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:57:28.000Z","msg":"賠錢呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d019cda420074aacf1ea96af5c2bba007ad6b273","tid":1317620,"uid":122988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:03:17.000Z","msg":"[和理非召喚]齊齊向盧偉聰追數 2.0 (小額錢債審裁處)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243873</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n參考下"},{"pid":"7fe7bc078d604a94cb5b8641ea54d69ce62b574b","tid":1317620,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:03:35.000Z","msg":"一齊告佢老母搞到我地精神創傷。<br />\n等佢無穿無爛得咁開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf74b6c2162a6361cff38f301c79553082cf9b8","tid":1317620,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e981dabc527da06de57f30521b78e8f7b1364e6","tid":1317620,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:48:39.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}